{"thag3.7:0.1":"Theragatha 3.7 ","thag3.7:0.2":"Tikanipata ","thag3.7:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag3.7:0.4":"Varanattheragatha ","thag3.7:1.1":"“Yodha koci manussesu, ","thag3.7:1.2":"parapanani himsati; ","thag3.7:1.3":"Asma loka paramha ca, ","thag3.7:1.4":"ubhaya dhamsate naro. ","thag3.7:2.1":"Yo ca mettena cittena, ","thag3.7:2.2":"sabbapananukampati; ","thag3.7:2.3":"Bahunhi so pasavati, ","thag3.7:2.4":"punnam tadisako naro. ","thag3.7:3.1":"Subhasitassa sikkhetha, ","thag3.7:3.2":"samanupasanassa ca; ","thag3.7:3.3":"Ekasanassa ca raho, ","thag3.7:3.4":"cittavupasamassa ca”ti. ","thag3.7:3.5":"… Varano thero …. "}